articles.title: Mitchell Marsh & Glenn Maxwell Ruled Out; Here's Australia's Playing XI Vs England - OneCricket
articles.description: In a massive setback for Australia, two premier all-rounders, Glenn Maxwell and Mitchell Marsh have been ruled out of the all-important World Cup clash against arch-rivals England in Ahmedabad.
